{"tid":2154830,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［唔使東江水？！］澳洲太陽能海水化淡 海水曬30分鐘後可飲用","createTime":"2020-08-13T10:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T10:44:50.000Z","uid":48083,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6ba37b6eea5f2343e4d20dbf4dc72ebfdbfc5e","tid":2154830,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:55:45.000Z","msg":"據悉， 最近一個由澳洲蒙納殊大學 ( Monash University ) 所領導的國際研究團隊研發出最新的太陽能海水化淡技術，能夠透過一種金屬有機框架材料 ( MOF ) 過濾海水中的污染物，從而生產大量淡水。而今次研究團隊開發出名為 PSP-MIL-53 的新型 MOF，可以捕捉海水和鹹水裡面的鹽與雜質。研究團隊表示，這種新型 MOF 的效率更高，所需能源也比較少。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JgTvzN6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJgTvzN6.jpg&h=28c32b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n研究團隊將 MOF 放入水中、曝曬陽光後，只要 30 分鐘左右就可將水中總溶解固體從 2,233 ppm 降至 500 ppm 以下，比 WHO 建議的安全飲用水標準 600 ppm 還低。研究人員又指出， 1 公斤 MOF 每天能生產 139.5 公升的淡水，而且清洗容易，只要放在陽光下 4 分鐘就能重複再利用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/13/australia-new-technology-turn-seawater-into-drinking-water-within-30-minutes/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F13%2Faustralia-new-technology-turn-seawater-into-drinking-water-within-30-minutes%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=d2bc597c\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/13/australia-new-technology-turn-seawater-into-drinking-water-within-30-minutes/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"210324124157cd7fdb185ff552f96ccf481e6a23","tid":2154830,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:57:03.000Z","msg":"咁西利！？"},{"pid":"79fc5ec1386dc6034846aa001e2ff8109a16d989","tid":2154830,"uid":295602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:57:33.000Z","msg":"如果佢舊野可以用得耐, 同埋唔容易contaminate, 咁聽落幾理想"},{"pid":"680b19ddf754477684d29d98da1c72df0d9998ac","tid":2154830,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:59:45.000Z","msg":"愚昧嘅我睇標題第一下諗下蒸餾技術<img src=\"